The paper is about automated program repair, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The approach proposed in the paper uses genetic programming (GP) to search for patches, which is a technique commonly used in programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of multi-objective optimization and test filtering, which are topics related to systems and control (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG).
